#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.54"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.54:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.54:0.2"
msgid "6. Brāhmaṇavagga"
msgstr "6. Brahmins"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.54:0.3"
msgid "54. Paribbājakasutta"
msgstr "54. A Wanderer"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.54:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho aññataro brāhmaṇaparibbājako yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; "
"upasaṅkamitvā … pe … ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so brāhmaṇaparibbājako "
"bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then a brahmin wanderer went up to the Buddha … Seated to one side he said "
"to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "an3.54:1.2"
msgid "“‘sandiṭṭhiko dhammo sandiṭṭhiko dhammo’ti, bho gotama, vuccati."
msgstr ""
"“Master Gotama, they speak of ‘a teaching realizable in this very life’."

msgctxt "an3.54:1.3"
msgid ""
"Kittāvatā nu kho, bho gotama, sandiṭṭhiko dhammo hoti akāliko ehipassiko "
"opaneyyiko paccattaṃ veditabbo viññūhī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"In what way is the teaching realizable in this very life, immediately "
"effective, inviting inspection, relevant, so that sensible people can know "
"it for themselves?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.54:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Ratto kho, brāhmaṇa, rāgena abhibhūto pariyādinnacitto attabyābādhāyapi "
"ceteti, parabyābādhāyapi ceteti, ubhayabyābādhāyapi ceteti, cetasikampi "
"dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr ""
"“A greedy person, overcome by greed, intends to hurt themselves, hurt "
"others, and hurt both. They experience mental pain and sadness."

msgctxt "an3.54:2.2"
msgid ""
"Rāge pahīne nevattabyābādhāyapi ceteti, na parabyābādhāyapi ceteti, na "
"ubhayabyābādhāyapi ceteti, na cetasikampi dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr ""
"When greed has been given up, they don’t intend to hurt themselves, hurt "
"others, and hurt both. They don’t experience mental pain and sadness."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli1.158"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an3.54:3.1"
msgid ""
"Ratto kho, brāhmaṇa, rāgena abhibhūto pariyādinnacitto kāyena duccaritaṃ "
"carati, vācāya duccaritaṃ carati, manasā duccaritaṃ carati."
msgstr "A greedy person does bad things by way of body, speech, and mind."

msgctxt "an3.54:3.2"
msgid ""
"Rāge pahīne neva kāyena duccaritaṃ carati, na vācāya duccaritaṃ carati, na "
"manasā duccaritaṃ carati."
msgstr ""
"When greed has been given up, they don’t do bad things by way of body, "
"speech, and mind."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an3.54:4.1"
msgid ""
"Ratto kho, brāhmaṇa, rāgena abhibhūto pariyādinnacitto attatthampi "
"yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti, paratthampi yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti, ubhayatthampi "
"yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti."
msgstr ""
"A greedy person doesn’t truly understand what’s for their own good, the good "
"of another, or the good of both."

msgctxt "an3.54:4.2"
msgid ""
"Rāge pahīne attatthampi yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, paratthampi yathābhūtaṃ "
"pajānāti, ubhayatthampi yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr ""
"When greed has been given up, they truly understand what’s for their own "
"good, the good of another, or the good of both."

msgctxt "an3.54:4.3"
msgid "Evampi kho, brāhmaṇa, sandiṭṭhiko dhammo hoti … pe …."
msgstr ""
"This is how the teaching is realizable in this very life, immediately "
"effective, inviting inspection, relevant, so that sensible people can know "
"it for themselves."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an3.54:5.1"
msgid "Duṭṭho kho, brāhmaṇa, dosena … pe …"
msgstr "A hateful person …"

msgctxt "an3.54:5.2"
msgid ""
"mūḷho kho, brāhmaṇa, mohena abhibhūto pariyādinnacitto attabyābādhāyapi "
"ceteti, parabyābādhāyapi ceteti, ubhayabyābādhāyapi ceteti, cetasikampi "
"dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr ""
"A deluded person, overcome by delusion, intends to hurt themselves, hurt "
"others, and hurt both. They experience mental pain and sadness."

msgctxt "an3.54:5.3"
msgid ""
"Mohe pahīne nevattabyābādhāyapi ceteti, na parabyābādhāyapi ceteti, na "
"ubhayabyābādhāyapi ceteti, na cetasikaṃ dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr ""
"When delusion has been given up, they don’t intend to hurt themselves, hurt "
"others, and hurt both. They don’t experience mental pain and sadness."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an3.54:6.1"
msgid ""
"Mūḷho kho, brāhmaṇa, mohena abhibhūto pariyādinnacitto, kāyena duccaritaṃ "
"carati, vācāya duccaritaṃ carati, manasā duccaritaṃ carati."
msgstr "A deluded person does bad things by way of body, speech, and mind."

msgctxt "an3.54:6.2"
msgid ""
"Mohe pahīne neva kāyena duccaritaṃ carati, na vācāya duccaritaṃ carati, na "
"manasā duccaritaṃ carati."
msgstr ""
"When delusion has been given up, they don’t do bad things by way of body, "
"speech, and mind."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an3.54:7.1"
msgid ""
"Mūḷho kho, brāhmaṇa, mohena abhibhūto pariyādinnacitto attatthampi "
"yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti, paratthampi yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti, ubhayatthampi "
"yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti."
msgstr ""
"A deluded person doesn’t truly understand what’s for their own good, the "
"good of another, or the good of both."

msgctxt "an3.54:7.2"
msgid ""
"Mohe pahīne attatthampi yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti, paratthampi yathābhūtaṃ "
"pajānāti, ubhayatthampi yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr ""
"When delusion has been given up, they truly understand what’s for their own "
"good, the good of another, or the good of both."

msgctxt "an3.54:7.3"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, sandiṭṭhiko dhammo hoti akāliko ehipassiko opaneyyiko "
"paccattaṃ veditabbo viññūhī”ti."
msgstr ""
"This, too, is how the teaching is realizable in this very life, immediately "
"effective, inviting inspection, relevant, so that sensible people can know "
"it for themselves.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an3.54:8.1"
msgid "“Abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe …"
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent!"

msgctxt "an3.54:8.2"
msgid ""
"upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.54:8.3"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
